![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/17981582-6d94-4fb1-baf8-4c2e63ae6604/e337.jpg)

Step into the world of '90s comics nostalgia with us as we revisit "Rise of Apocalypse," the epic Marvel series that introduced one of its most notorious villains. Join us for a lively discussion as we unpack Apocalypse's origins, his quest for power, and the heroes who dared to challenge him. From the wild art style to the epic battles, we dive into what made this series a fan favorite and why it still holds up today. Whether you're a die-hard comic fan or just curious about '90s pop culture, this episode promises to be a fun ride through mutant mayhem and cosmic chaos!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  

